RUN: not %COMPILE --error-format clang build plc.json 2>&1 | %CHECK %s

An unwired in_out is emitted as an empty argument, which the main pipeline
rejects — an in_out parameter must be a real reference.
CHECK: {{.*}}function_inout_unwired.cfc:{{.*}}error[E031]: Expected a reference for parameter acc because their type is InOut
CHECK: error: Compilation aborted due to critical errors
